Analysis of surgical and oncological outcome in internal and external 
hemipelvectomy in 34 patients above the age of 65 years at a mean follow-up of 
56 months.

Guder WK(1), Hardes J(2), Gosheger G(3), Henrichs MP(4), Nottrott M(5), 
Streitbürger A(6).

Author information:
(1)Department of Orthopedics and Tumor Orthopedics, University Hospital 
